<p>Simple Mini Map package includes the easy-to-use MiniMap feature. It contains very little code.</p>



<p><a href="https://github.com/bilal-arikan/UnitySimpleMiniMap">https://github.com/bilal-arikan/UnitySimpleMiniMap</a></p>



<p><a href="https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/slug/226420">https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/slug/226420</a></p>



