<ul>
<li>You can import MiniMapDemo.unitypackage to review the example in the video</li>
</ul>



<ul>
<li>How to Use:</li>
</ul>



<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>var minimap = FindObjectOfType&lt;Arikan.MiniMapView>();

// Red object example
var img = minimap.FollowCentered(obj1Centered.transform);
img.color = obj1Centered.material.color;

// Green object example
var img2 = minimap.Follow(obj2.transform);
img2.color = obj2.material.color;

// Blue object example
var img3 = minimap.Follow(obj3.transform, obj3Sprite);
img3.color = obj3.material.color;</code></pre>



